OL,3,CLoyalist Irvine jailed but 'peace'
OL,4,Cefforts see him escape five-year term
OL,6,FThe offences were committed on June 8,
OL,7,F2022 when Workman transported a
OL,8,Fquantity of weapons and ammunition to
OL,9,Fthe Glencairn area of Belfast in his
OL,10,Fvan, which were then put into the boot
OL,11,Fof Irvine's Volkswagen Tiguan car.
OL,13,FA short time later Irvine's vehicle
OL,14,Fwas stopped by police in Disraeli
OL,15,FStreet.
OL,17,FA long-barrelled firearm, two
OL,18,Fsuspected pistols, several magazines
OL,19,Fand a large quantity of ammunition
OL,20,Fwere discovered inside a bag in the
OL,21,Fboot.
