OL,3,CLoyalist Irvine jailed but 'peace'
OL,4,Cefforts see him escape five-year term
OL,6,FSeveral references crediting Irvine
OL,7,Ffor peacebuilding work in Northern
OL,8,FIreland were submitted by his legal
OL,9,Fteam, including from David Campbell,
OL,10,Fchairman of the Loyalist Communities
OL,11,FCouncil (LCC), and former Northern
OL,12,FIreland Policing Board member Debbie
OL,13,FWatters.
OL,15,FJudge Kerr said he had taken into
OL,16,Faccount the references praising
OL,17,FIrvine's work in the community when
OL,18,Fassessing whether the case involved
OL,19,Fexceptional circumstances.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
