OL,3,CLoyalist Irvine jailed but 'peace'
OL,4,Cefforts see him escape five-year term
OL,6,F"I do consider a combination of the
OL,7,Fmatters relating to the defendant do
OL,8,Freach a level which could be described
OL,9,Fas exceptional, in particular the
OL,10,Fdefendant's work for peace and charity
OL,11,Fwork in the community," he said.
OL,13,FHe said it would therefore not be
OL,14,Fproper to impose the statutory five-
OL,15,Fyear sentence.
